UPDATE salons SET reviews='[{"author":"Neelam","rating":5,"text":"Excellent and exclusive.","date":"Oct 2022"},{"author":"Shruti","rating":5,"text":"Thank You Gaur Sir and Lilly Ma''am for making my dream gown a real one, I must say you ppl deal a bride not as a customer but you pay attention as a responsible team to make us feel wow and confident!! My family was really amazed after listening to the cost of it and seeing the material you used words couldn''t describe what I''m really feeling May God bless you and your team you guys are a true blessing Highly recommended for all the brides who want to make their special day a memorable one As to a family there is one family doctor to our family you are from now our family gown provider.","date":"Oct 2019"},{"author":"Lalita","rating":4.5,"text":"The best reception and cocktail party gown available highly recommend very reasonable prices","date":"Jun 2019"},{"author":"Prashant","rating":5,"text":"Latest range available, awesome collection & m very happy with their service. I really appreciate them.","date":"Jan 2019"},{"author":"Sana","rating":4.5,"text":"I love the colour gowns collection please keep updating us when new collection is out","date":"Nov 2018"},{"author":"Vineet","rating":5,"text":"I am very happy with your service My sister was in love with the dress you made for her, The delivery and process was great within 7 days the dress was with us Wish you great success ahead.","date":"Apr 2016"}]'::jsonb WHERE id='0497b94e-119d-4eb0-976a-b858328e8f2e';
UPDATE salons SET reviews='[{"author":"Kusum","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Apr 2023"},{"author":"Anubha","rating":4.5,"text":"I would highly recommend this for someone passionate about the fashion industry. It''s an Amazing experience too deepen inside the fashion world, through history, design and concept of dresses the customer service and all salesman are so humble in nature ... truly no one can say ''No to the dress","date":"Nov 2020"},{"author":"Bella","rating":5,"text":"My Wedding Dress was made by Payal keyal, . salesman let me explain my vision for both the events and then suggested the outfits, blouse design and dupatta design for the wedding. Even though it was such a heavy piece, they delivered on time!","date":"Nov 2020"},{"author":"Gia","rating":4.5,"text":"I''m from Canada and I purchased my lehenga on virtual appointment. Their staff and salesperson treat me very well I really like their payal Keyal outfits and I purchased my lehenga from Payal keyal collection only","date":"Nov 2020"},{"author":"Sneha","rating":5,"text":"Collection was so good their marwar collection was so different . I never seen that amazingswork on any lehengas . i was so happy after purchasing my stuff from this store","date":"Nov 2020"},{"author":"Shailesh","rating":3,"text":"Must visit.","date":"Jun 2014"}]'::jsonb WHERE id='1a08d263-6d5a-44e3-a023-802487bfee48';
