UPDATE salons SET reviews='[{"author":"Javed","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Nov 2020"},{"author":"Neetu","rating":5,"text":"I got my engagement outfit from them and they were really good at their work. They have a huge collection and all the designs look lovely.The place offers a variety of bridal trousseau options for the bride and the bridesmaids. Delivery is also timely done and you can easily get what you''re looking for. My outfit looked really pretty and it was what I wanted!","date":"Sep 2019"},{"author":"Neetu","rating":5,"text":"Beautiful and amazing collection of ethnic and wedding dresses. I have personally bought 3 lehengas from this place, and I am very happy with my choices. Thank you, Kala Shree Regalia.","date":"Aug 2019"},{"author":"Smriti","rating":5,"text":"These people have amazing variety at genuine prices.Recommended for brides","date":"May 2017"},{"author":"Anvi","rating":5,"text":"They have all types of variety and not only the collection but prices are also very genuine. Recommendable place for wedding trousseau shopping.","date":"Jun 2015"},{"author":"Dhanshree","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Apr 2013"}]'::jsonb WHERE id='3ed92bb6-eed7-4217-86f1-cfbff4651407';
UPDATE salons SET reviews='[{"author":"Lakshmi","rating":5,"text":"I am coming from past 15 to 20 years to roop Vatika they have got beautiful beautiful collection of suits Sarees gowns drape Sarees this is the one stop shop for every wedding Jab Bhi there is some occasion at my place i always visit Roop Vatika and they never disappoint me and I always visit them and they look after me so well Kuch na kuch to pasand aata hi hai as they have got lot of beautiful options of everything..","date":"Apr 2026"},{"author":"Mamta","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Oct 2025"},{"author":"Akansha","rating":5,"text":"Roop Vatika is a fantastic place for clothing and accessories. The fitting of the clothes is very good, and they offer custom tailoring to make sure everything fits perfectly. The staff is very helpful and friendly specailly kavita and nikita maam making the shopping experience enjoyable. The ambience of the store is vibrant, which adds to the fun atmosphere. The management is excellent, ensuring everything runs smoothly. Overall, Roop Vatika is a great choice for stylish and well-fitting clothes!","date":"Aug 2025"},{"author":"Shweta","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Dec 2024"},{"author":"Sumit","rating":5,"text":"We were assured that if we didn''t like the outfit we would be welcomed to get it return as well but they didn''t informed that we could say no to any of the dress as every dress was made with such beautiful work and handcrafted embroidery which was just like cherry on cake.","date":"Feb 2023"},{"author":"Kashish","rating":5,"text":"Exquisite designs and details. Great for Shaadi shopping , must check it out during the wedding season. The store matches the designs and quality of high end designers , if you are on a hunt for your shaadi shopping , this is the place for you. A must visit for all brides to be , the collection and quality is top notch. The staff is kind and helpful and will help you find your perfect fit","date":"Feb 2023"}]'::jsonb WHERE id='4fd4784f-f76d-4ea1-8148-e2f2cb59b60a';
UPDATE salons SET reviews='[{"author":"Vansh","rating":5,"text":"We have been here for 4 -5 times. Awesome n designer unique dresses n the Staff here is very much sweet, Especially @ Anshul . She has always been very humble, polite n Cooperative with her ever smiling face. Very much happy to be happy customer","date":"Aug 2023"},{"author":"Arsheen","rating":5,"text":"","date":"Jul 2022"},{"author":"Ansh","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Mar 2022"},{"author":"Raghav","rating":3,"text":"","date":"Jul 2017"},{"author":"Isha","rating":5,"text":"Excellent","date":"Dec 2014"},{"author":"Rakhi","rating":4,"text":"Very Good","date":"Jun 2014"}]'::jsonb WHERE id='571f0f35-1fd1-4761-bfb5-5460e8029d6c';
